hopobject.body: I've been made redundant achat viagra france What cannot be questioned is that Key’s tweet instantly stencilled itself on the honours board of memorable reflex reactions to sporting high drama. It had been a good while since grave disappointment provoked a public show of cussing. We have to go back almost three weeks to Sept 7, 2013, in fact, when, after losing a US Open semi-final he had led by two sets to one, a gallant Stanislas Wawrinka praised his conqueror in the post-match interview by describing Novak Djokovic as “f------ strong”.
